(747, 42, 'Wondering where to go in Cambodia that is popular yet peaceful. Consider the Siem Reap river and the rice paddies make this town much more than just a stopover to witness the Angkor temples.', 'http://itourscloud.com/destination_gallery/asia/combodia/The-cultural-tourist-hub-of-Siem-Reap-04.jpg'),
(748, 42, 'Explore the innumerable temples at Koh Ker that lies to the northeast of the Siem reap town.', 'http://itourscloud.com/destination_gallery/asia/combodia/The-beautiful-Koh-Ker-temple-05.jpg'),
(749, 42, 'Phnom Penh still retains its charm as the leafy capital city of Cambodia with its palaces and wats.', 'http://itourscloud.com/destination_gallery/asia/combodia/The-Royal-Palace-in-Phnom-Penh-06.jpg'),
(750, 42, 'One of Cambodia?s greatest tourist attractions, the Angkor Wat temple lies in Angkor and is one of the largest religious monuments to behold.', 'http://itourscloud.com/destination_gallery/asia/combodia/Angkor-wat-temple-complex-07.jpg'),
(751, 42, 'This is the capital of the largest city in central Cambodia. Just 11 km away from the Cambodian capital, Krong Ta Khmau is one of the best places to see in Cambodia if you are on a leisure trip.', 'http://itourscloud.com/destination_gallery/asia/combodia/Ta-Khmau-08.jpg'),
(752, 42, 'One of the most beautiful places in Cambodia, those looking for adventure will absolutely love the island paradise Koh Rong that has a number of beaches like the Koh Toch beach.', 'http://itourscloud.com/destination_gallery/asia/combodia/Plankton-at-Koh-Rong-09.jpg'),
(753, 42, 'Located in the eastern part of Cambodia, Mondulkiri is an interesting place to visit in Cambodia due to its abundant wildlife and natural beauty.', 'http://itourscloud.com/destination_gallery/asia/combodia/Tourists-at-Bou-Sra-Waterfall-10.jpg'),
(754, 43, 'As a place of the former political centre of the country for 13 uninterrupted centuries, Imperial Citadel of Thang Long is one of the most famous Vietnam tourist spots.', 'http://itourscloud.com/destination_gallery/asia/vietnam/Imperial-Citadel-of-Thang-Long-01.jpg'),
(755, 43, 'One of the most famous places to visit in Vietnam, Ho Chi Minh?s Mausoleum is a piece of spectacular marble construction, built with materials collected from all over the country.', 'http://itourscloud.com/destination_gallery/asia/vietnam/ho-chi-minh-mausoleum-02.jpg'),
(756, 43, 'If you are traveling with your family and want to spend a day with fun and laughter this is the place where you should head towards.', 'http://itourscloud.com/destination_gallery/asia/vietnam/hoan-kiem-lake-e1547532395556-03.jpg'),
(757, 43, 'This museum in Vietnam is one of the few that are based on the various ethnic groups of the country', 'http://itourscloud.com/destination_gallery/asia/vietnam/ethnology-04.jpg'),
(758, 43, 'This history museum is amongst the 7 national museums in the country of Vietnam. If you have a thing for military weapons, then this place is a must visit for people like you.', 'http://itourscloud.com/destination_gallery/asia/vietnam/Aircraft_wreckage-05.jpg');
